      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is governed by a documented software quality plan including version control, regression test suite, and release validation. All relevant SQA activities for Gradation 2 are satisfied."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
