      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via method-of-manufactured-solutions or equivalent benchmark.",
      "rationale": "Numerical code verification was performed against published FDA benchmark CFD results and internal manufactured-solution tests for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver. Results are within expected tolerances."
    },
    {
