      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported and discretization error must be bounded within acceptable limits for the hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted using meshes of 4.2M, 8.7M, and 17.1M cells. GCI for the hemolysis index QoI was 3.1%, satisfying the required level and exceeding it by one gradation."
