      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation must be documented and traceable to device operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions (flow rate 2.5–7.5 L/min, rotational speed 2000–3500 RPM) are fully documented with traceable measurement uncertainty. Conditions span the intended CPB operating envelope."
