      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, detailed characterization of biological test sample variability is not required.",
      "rationale": "The FDA benchmark used bovine blood with documented hematocrit range. Sample-to-sample biological variability characterization is not required at MRL 2 and was not assessed."
