    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out or not assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This determination is consistent with published applications of this model in clinical research contexts.",
